Vermont Yankee Pager Info Request Cc PST Don Below is the information that I need from Arch Wireless to have Enron up and running on the pager system for Vermont Yankee Contact Properties Contact Name Im assuming thats going to be you If you are not going to be holding the pager at all times then we may want to have a generic contact name Pager IDPin Please verify if I need to use all digits do I need hyphens Carrier Name Phone Number This needs to be a or number Max Characters Service Type Alpha or Numeric Baud Rate Settings We use AirSource Pro Software and the modem settings are as follows Gateway Telepath Modem Commands ATFKNEX The modem commands are not carrier specific so I need the command string to be compatible with the following carriers Rinkers CVC Paging Arch Contact The backup system weve put in place has the following modem settings Gateway Telepath II Fax Modem ATCDKMNQV I hope this helps regarding the information Hope its not too overwhelming Please contact me at or via email if you have any questions Thanks again for your help Id like to have this up and runner by the end of next week Take Care Bobbi J Kilburn Treasury Risk Administrator Vermont Yankee Nuclear Power Corporation
